#   Search: strip-ansi-escapes < <base>.log | grep ...
#   Opt out: export NO_SCRIPT_LOG=1  (before the shell starts)
# Re-execs the shell under script; the inner shell skips this block via
# the SHELL_SESSION_LOG guard. Non-interactive shells (agents, scp) are skipped.
